#Approach:

Maximum Subarray – Kadane’s Algorithm

Is problem me hume continuous subarray ka maximum sum find karna hota hai.
Iske liye hum Kadane’s Algorithm use karte hain.

Hum ek running sum maintain karte hain.
Array traverse karte waqt har element ko running sum me add karte hain
aur har step par maximum sum update karte rehte hain.

Agar running sum kabhi negative ho jaye, to usse 0 kar dete hain
kyunki negative sum future subarray ko chhota hi karega, bada nahi.

Isliye jab sum negative ho jaye to new subarray start karna better hota hai.

End me jo maximum sum mila hoga wahi maximum subarray sum hoga.

Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(1)

#Code:

class Solution {
    public int maxSubArray(int[] nums) {
        int sum = 0;
        int maxi = Integer.MIN_VALUE;

        for(int i=0; i<nums.length; i++){
            sum += nums[i];
            maxi = Math.max(maxi, sum);

            if(sum < 0){
                sum = 0;
            }
        }

        return maxi;
    }
}
